            <div class="article_col-main article_col-main-left article_main">
              <div class="article-body" itemprop="articleBody">
                    <p> Meet the Press - March 27, 2016 </p>
                
              
              
              
                    <p> CHUCK TODD: </p>
                
              
              
              
                    <p> This Sunday, terror in Brussels, after another horrific ISIS attack on yet another European capital, are major intelligence failings putting more lives at risk? </p>
                
              
              
              
                    <p> RICHARD ENGEL: </p>
                
              
              
              
                    <p> This country seems overwhelmed by the scale of the threat. </p>
                
              
                    <div class="ad-container ad-container_default ad-container_mobile ad-hide">
                      <div class="ad-label ad-hide">
                      	<a href="http://www.nbcnews.com/id/31066137/media-kit/" target="_blank">advertisement</a>
                      </div>
                      <div class="ad-content ad-xs box1" data-placement="box1"></div>
                    </div>
              
              
                    <p> CHUCK TODD: </p>
                
              
              
              
                    <p> We'll have the latest from a city on edge. Plus, the Trump effect. The Republican race devolves even further, if that was possible, with a Trump/Cruz feud over the candidates' wives. </p>
                
              
              
              
